Phase 1A - Replacement mode and compile gate (`@ios-dev`)

- [x] Apply code replacement only for `VenuesVC`/`VenuesMigration` scope in this feature pass.
- [x] After each replacement chunk, run compile check and resolve build errors before continuing.
